data.description: Your Port Orange Oasis awaits... Welcome home to Hawks Ridge, a small community located in the heart of one of the safest cities in Florida.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom pool home has had almost every update imaginable in the last 5 years, (Pool resurfaced 2019, pool pump 2020, new screen porches and screen pool enclosure 2018, Chattahoochee pebble stone pool deck and paver walkway 2018, irrigation pump 2023, interior and exterior paint 2022, both complete bathroom remodels 2018,  large tile throughout entire home 2018, garage door opener and springs 2022, sliding glass door 2020, A/C 2017, complete kitchen remodel including Kraftmaid cabinets with soft close door and drawers, Blue Pearl Granite countertops in 2021 and a complete appliance package including washer and dryer.  Roof 10/2023. The seller is also including 5 Samsung wall mounted tv's and the outside sound system for enjoying days out by the pool.  Let's make this your home.
